  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad atbildeja Gada Behr- ni/ un Ruhbera Behrni/ un faz- zija: Ko tas KUNGSus taweem Kalpeem runnajis irr/ ta darri- sim mehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mehs eefim apbrunno- ti pahri KUNGA Preekshâ us Ranaâna Semmi/ un muhfo ee- mantojamu Jhpaachunu turre- sim mehs Schaipufs Jardanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad dewe Mohsus win- neein teem Gada Behrneem/ un teem Ruhbera Behrneem/ un tai puſs Zilti Manaffus/ Jahsepa Dehla/ to Walstibu Siona/ ta Amoriteru Kehnina/ un to Wal- stibu Oga/ ta Bahsana Kehnina/ to Semmi ar teem Pilfsahteem/ lihds ar winno Rohbeschahm/ ar tahs Semnes Pilfsahteem wiſ- apfahrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Gada Behrni uſ- taiſija Dibonn/ un Atarotu/ un Arweru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Atarot-Soweru/ un Jaeseru/un Jegabeu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Bet-Nimru/ un Be- faranu/ stiprus Pilfsahtus/ un jihu Lohpu Laidarus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Ruhbera Behrni uſtaiſija Esbonn/ un Eeleali/ un Kiriataimu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Nebu/un Baal-Meo- nu ar zitteem Wahrdeem/ un Sibamn/ un tee noſauze tohs Pilfsahtus/ ko tee uſtaiſija ar zit- teem Wahrdeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Makira Behrni/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "juhfu Starpâ fawu Jhpaachunu dabbuht Ranaâna Semmê.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tà dewe Mohsus Gilea- du Makiram/ Manaffus Deh- lam/ un wiꞥſch dsihwoja eekſch tahs bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jairs Manaffus Dehls gahje/ un uſneeme winnu Zee- mus/ un noſauze tohs Awot- Jairu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Nohbus gahje/ un uſ- nehine Knatu/ ar winnas peeder- rigahm Weetahm/ un noſauze Nohbu pehz fawu Wahrdn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Manaffus Dehla/ gahje us Gi- leadu/ un uſnehme to/ un iſdsin- ne tohs Amoriterus/ kas eekſch tahs bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "TA XXXIII. Nodalla.\nMohsus stahsta tohs Zettus nn Mahjaweetaß to Israëta Behrnu no Egiptes/ us to apfohlitu Ranaâna Semmi/ lihds Jardanai: 1. Aã- roza Wezzunas un Mirschana: 38/39. Tas KUNGS pawehf tohs Kananiterus iſdsiht: 50/51. Lihds ar to Likstu/ kas pakkat buhs/ kad tee tai Semmê paliks: 55/56.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Chee irr to Israëta Behrnu Zetta-Gahju- mi/ kas no Egiptes- Semnes irr iſgahjuſchi/ pehz winnu Pulkeem/ zaar Mohsu un Aäronu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mohsus aprakſtija win- no Iseefchanu pehz winno Zetta- Gahjumeem/ us ta KUNGA Wahrdn/ un chee irr winnu Zet- ta-Gahjumi/ winneem iſeijoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee iſgahje no Raïnses pir- mâ Mehneti/ peektâpadeſmitâ Deenâ/ pirnâ Mehneti ohtrâ Paſfa-Swechtku Deenâ iſgahje tee Israëta Behrni/ zaar weena angſtu\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
